com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel.sunrise.api

Class Port

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel.sunrise.api.Port
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IExpressionSegment
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    InPort, OutPort

    public abstract class Port
extends Object
implements IExpressionSegment
    A port is a Data-Flow-Element (DFE) in a SPR. Ports belong to parents and can be connected with Assignments.
    This element is an undocumented internal feature. It is not intended to be used by applications as it might change or be removed in future versions.
